  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicWalker
    Simple enemy, has a Chasing Behavior.
    EnemyController
    Creates a default Enemy, to be fully implemented by the methods of the specific enemy types.
    EntityController
    The Default Entity for all controllers.
    FlyingEnemy
    Flying enemy, extends from a default Enemy, has a flying behavior associated.
    HeroController
    The hero of the game.
    HeroWin
    Custom hero, created only when the player wins.
    PowerupController
    The controller for the powerup to be spawned, houses all the different powerup types.
    ProjectileController  
    ToughEnemy
    Tough enemy, extends from a default Enemy, has a tough behavior associated.
